    <img src='/images/logos/immutant_icon_256px_flipped.png' id='gil' title='Gil' alt='Gil' align='right'/>

    Immutant is an application server for
    [Clojure](http://clojure.org). It's an integrated platform built
    on [JBoss AS7](http://www.jboss.org/as7) providing support for
    [Ring](https://github.com/ring-clojure/ring) handlers, asynchronous
    messaging, caching, scheduled jobs, XA transactions, clustering,
    daemons and more!
    
    We provide a [Leiningen](http://leiningen.org/) [plugin](https://github.com/immutant/lein-immutant)
    that makes [installing](/install/) and managing an Immutant simple.

    Have questions or want to get involved? Come see us in [IRC](/community/#irc) or join our 
    [mailing lists](/community/mailing_lists/).
